# Docker & Infrastructure Rules

## Dockerfiles
- Multi-stage builds for Go services (builder + alpine runtime)
- Slim base images for Python (python:3.13-slim)
- Alpine base for Node.js (node:22-alpine)
- Non-root user in production images
- COPY dependency files first for layer caching
- .dockerignore in each service directory

## Docker Compose
- Version: services at top level (compose v2 format)
- Health checks on all services
- Named volumes for persistent data
- Single network (orion-net) for service communication
- env_file for configuration
- Profiles for optional services (gpu, monitoring)

## Naming
- Service names match directory names (lowercase, no underscores)
- Volume names: {service}data (e.g., pgdata, redisdata)
- Network: orion-net
